text: Jan Hendrik Albert "Henny" Eman (20 March 1948 - 6 January 2025) was an Aruban retired politician. He was the first Prime Minister of Aruba from 1 January 1986 to 9 February 1989 and again from 29 July 1994 to 30 October 2001. Eman died on 6 January 2025, at the age of 76. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:2025 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Aruba
